Even better, try to get
people in Iran and Israel

00:46:06.322 --> 00:46:07.658
to interact with each other,

00:46:07.658 --> 00:46:10.003
or Pakistan and India to
interact with each other.

00:46:10.003 --> 00:46:11.805
That is very tangible world peace.

00:46:11.805 --> 00:46:13.405
That's something that you can go home,

00:46:13.405 --> 00:46:15.557
right now, and do from your living room.

00:46:15.557 --> 00:46:19.347
