00:47:17.740 --> 00:47:19.652
without governmental support,

00:47:19.652 --> 00:47:21.588
to start something that has the potential,

00:47:21.588 --> 00:47:22.988
over the next 5-10 years,

00:47:22.988 --> 00:47:25.115
to touch millions of people.

00:47:25.115 --> 00:47:27.717
Even if it doesn't touch millions
